'''''The Boy from Ipanema''''' ({{ko-hhrm|이파네마 소년||Ipanema Sonyeon}} is a 2010 [[South Korea]]n [[independent film|independent]] [[teen film|teen]] [[fantasy film|fantasy]] [[romance film]] filmed in [[Busan]] and [[Sapporo]].<ref>{{cite web|title=The Boy from Ipanema (2010)|url=http://english.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2010/11/05/2010110500835.html|website=[[The Chosun Ilbo]]|accessdate=2015-11-06|date=5 January 2010}}</ref>

==Cast==
* [[Lee Soo-hyuk]] as Boy
* [[Kim Min-ji (actress)|Kim Min-ji]] as Girl
* [[Chun Woo-hee]] as Friend

==Awards==
*[[Jeonju International Film Festival#11th Jeonju International Film Festival (2010)|2010 Jeonju International Film Festival]]: Audience Critic's Award<ref>{{cite web|title=JIFF 2010 Wrap-Up|url=http://www.koreanfilm.org/tom/?p=1261|website=Seen In Jeonju|accessdate=2015-11-06|date=12 May 2010}}</ref> 
*[[Jeonju International Film Festival#11th Jeonju International Film Festival (2010)|2010 Jeonju International Film Festival]]: Movie Collage Award

